description:
This is a bonus product.
Note: Available until February 28th, 2022.

■Contents
Zhao Yun is added under the following armor types in Male Custom Parts.
Helmet Type / Chest Type / Waist Type / Arm Type / Leg Type

■To Use
In Edit Mode, select Male from Gender, and then select the content from the corresponding type of armor.

Note: Please note that some of these might be made available for separate purchase at a later time.
name: Male Custom Zhao Yun Set
